{"thi-ap23:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap23:0.2":"Kundalakesivagga ","thi-ap23:0.3":"Dhammadinnatheriapadana ","thi-ap23:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","thi-ap23:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","thi-ap23:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","thi-ap23:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","thi-ap23:2.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","thi-ap23:2.2":"kule annatare ahum; ","thi-ap23:2.3":"Parakammakari asim, ","thi-ap23:2.4":"nipaka silasamvuta. ","thi-ap23:3.1":"Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","thi-ap23:3.2":"sujato aggasavako; ","thi-ap23:3.3":"Vihara abhinikkhamma, ","thi-ap23:3.4":"pindapataya gacchati. ","thi-ap23:4.1":"Ghatam gahetva gacchanti, ","thi-ap23:4.2":"tada udakaharika; ","thi-ap23:4.3":"Tam disva adadam pupam, ","thi-ap23:4.4":"pasanna sehi panibhi. ","thi-ap23:5.1":"Patiggahetva tattheva, ","thi-ap23:5.2":"nisinno paribhunji so; ","thi-ap23:5.3":"Tato netvana tam geham, ","thi-ap23:5.4":"adasim tassa bhojanam. ","thi-ap23:6.1":"Tato me ayyako tuttho, ","thi-ap23:6.2":"akari sunisam sakam; ","thi-ap23:6.3":"Sassuya saha gantvana, ","thi-ap23:6.4":"sambuddham abhivadayim. ","thi-ap23:7.1":"Tada so dhammakathikam, ","thi-ap23:7.2":"bhikkhunim parikittayam; ","thi-ap23:7.3":"Thapesi etadaggamhi, ","thi-ap23:7.4":"tam sutva mudita aham. ","thi-ap23:8.1":"Nimantayitva sugatam, ","thi-ap23:8.2":"sasangham lokanayakam; ","thi-ap23:8.3":"Mahadanam daditvana, ","thi-ap23:8.4":"tam thanamabhipatthayim. ","thi-ap23:9.1":"Tato mam sugato aha, ","thi-ap23:9.2":"ghananinnadasussaro; ","thi-ap23:9.3":"‘Mamupatthananirate, ","thi-ap23:9.4":"sasanghaparivesike. ","thi-ap23:10.1":"Saddhammassavane yutte, ","thi-ap23:10.2":"gunavaddhitamanase; ","thi-ap23:10.3":"Bhadde bhavassu mudita, ","thi-ap23:10.4":"lacchase panidhiphalam. ","thi-ap23:11.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap23:11.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","thi-ap23:11.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","thi-ap23:11.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","thi-ap23:12.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayada, ","thi-ap23:12.2":"orasa dhammanimmita; ","thi-ap23:12.3":"Dhammadinnati namena, ","thi-ap23:12.4":"hessati satthu savika’. ","thi-ap23:13.1":"Tam sutva mudita hutva, ","thi-ap23:13.2":"yavajivam mahamunim; ","thi-ap23:13.3":"Mettacitta paricarim, ","thi-ap23:13.4":"paccayehi vinayakam. ","thi-ap23:14.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap23:14.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap23:14.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap23:14.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap23:15.1":"Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","thi-ap23:15.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","thi-ap23:15.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","thi-ap23:15.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","thi-ap23:16.1":"Upatthako mahesissa, ","thi-ap23:16.2":"tada asi narissaro; ","thi-ap23:16.3":"Kasiraja kiki nama, ","thi-ap23:16.4":"baranasipuruttame. ","thi-ap23:17.1":"Chattha tassasaham dhita, ","thi-ap23:17.2":"sudhamma iti vissuta; ","thi-ap23:17.3":"Dhammam sutva jinaggassa, ","thi-ap23:17.4":"pabbajjam samarocayim. ","thi-ap23:18.1":"Anujani na no tato, ","thi-ap23:18.2":"agareva tada mayam; ","thi-ap23:18.3":"Visavassasahassani, ","thi-ap23:18.4":"vicarimha atandita. ","thi-ap23:19.1":"Tatiyam bhanavaram. ","thi-ap23:20.1":"Komaribrahmacariyam, ","thi-ap23:20.2":"rajakanna sukhedhita; ","thi-ap23:20.3":"Buddhopatthananirata, ","thi-ap23:20.4":"mudita satta dhitaro. ","thi-ap23:21.1":"Samani samanagutta ca, ","thi-ap23:21.2":"bhikkhuni bhikkhudayika; ","thi-ap23:21.3":"Dhamma ceva sudhamma ca, ","thi-ap23:21.4":"sattami sanghadayika. ","thi-ap23:22.1":"Khema uppalavanna ca, ","thi-ap23:22.2":"patacara ca kundala; ","thi-ap23:22.3":"Gotami ca ahanceva, ","thi-ap23:22.4":"visakha hoti sattami. ","thi-ap23:23.1":"Tehi kammehi sukatehi, ","thi-ap23:23.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap23:23.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap23:23.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap23:24.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","thi-ap23:24.2":"giribbajapuruttame; ","thi-ap23:24.3":"Jata setthikule phite, ","thi-ap23:24.4":"sabbakamasamiddhine. ","thi-ap23:25.1":"Yada rupagunupeta, ","thi-ap23:25.2":"pathame yobbane thita; ","thi-ap23:25.3":"Tada parakulam gantva, ","thi-ap23:25.4":"vasim sukhasamappita. ","thi-ap23:26.1":"Upetva lokasaranam, ","thi-ap23:26.2":"sunitva dhammadesanam; ","thi-ap23:26.3":"Anagamiphalam patto, ","thi-ap23:26.4":"samiko me subuddhima. ","thi-ap23:27.1":"Tadaham anujanetva, ","thi-ap23:27.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","thi-ap23:27.3":"Na cireneva kalena, ","thi-ap23:27.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","thi-ap23:28.1":"Tada upasako so mam, ","thi-ap23:28.2":"upagantva apucchatha; ","thi-ap23:28.3":"Gambhire nipune panhe, ","thi-ap23:28.4":"te sabbe byakarim aham. ","thi-ap23:29.1":"Jino tasmim gune tuttho, ","thi-ap23:29.2":"etadagge thapesi mam; ","thi-ap23:29.3":"‘Bhikkhunim dhammakathikam, ","thi-ap23:29.4":"nannam passami edisim. ","thi-ap23:30.1":"Dhammadinna yatha dhira, ","thi-ap23:30.2":"evam dharetha bhikkhavo’; ","thi-ap23:30.3":"Evaham pandita homi, ","thi-ap23:30.4":"nayakenanukampita. ","thi-ap23:31.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thi-ap23:31.2":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thi-ap23:31.3":"Ohito garuko bharo, ","thi-ap23:31.4":"bhavanetti samuhata. ","thi-ap23:32.1":"Yassatthaya pabbajita, ","thi-ap23:32.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thi-ap23:32.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","thi-ap23:32.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhayo. ","thi-ap23:33.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homi, ","thi-ap23:33.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap23:33.3":"Paracittani janami, ","thi-ap23:33.4":"satthusasanakarika. ","thi-ap23:34.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap23:34.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap23:34.3":"Khepetva asave sabbe, ","thi-ap23:34.4":"visuddhasim sunimmala. ","thi-ap23:35.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap23:35.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap23:35.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap23:36.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap23:36.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap23:36.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap23:37.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap23:37.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap23:37.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap23:38.1":"Ittham sudam dhammadinna bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap23:39.1":"Dhammadinnatheriyapadanam tatiyam. "}